    "wizard_tone_select": "Poná how esalemi mateya ezali written • informative, lisapo, persuasive, humorous, to procedural. Oyo adjusts maloba, fraze structure, na engagement lolenge na match yo instructional tina.",
    "wizard_tone_select_title": "Kokoma mongongo",
    "wizard_length_select": "Tiá approximate maloba tángá mpo na esalemi mateya. Poná uta mokuse (200 maloba) mpo na noki reads na mozindo (2000 maloba) mpo na comprehensive coverage. Longer makomi allow mingi ndakisa na mike-mike.",
