    "onboarding_hint": "💡 Finá <strong>?</strong> anytime mpo na lisalisi!",
    "header_ai_backend": "Bobongisi ya AI Backend: Bongolá to poná yo preferred AI provider globally (e.g., Google Gemini, Anthropic Claude, OpenAI, to local Ollama). Oyo dictates which lolengel handles mpasi NLP tasks na bilembo ekeke across nyonso biloko ya mosala.",
    "header_analytics": "Bobongisi ya Analytics mpe Bonkutu. Talaka makomi ya bosaleli mpo na kotia telemetry. Na lolenge ya offline to FERPA, makambo nyonso ezali kobombama na masini ya yo.",
    "global_mute_toggle": "Universal mongongo mute bongolá. tángo enabled, nyonso mingongo ezali silenced elongo na: AI makomi-na-speech voices, AlloBot's typing bleeps na flight mingongo, browser fallback speech, lisano mongongo effects, na notification mingongo. Perfect mpo na quiet kelasirooms, testing environments, to tángo moyekoli need na work silently. bouton turns red na pulsing indicator tángo esalaka. mongongo automatically resumes tángo yo finá na unmute. Oyo bobongisi persists across lokasa reloads.",
    "glossary_standard_flashcards": "Sala flashcards ya maloba: pesa likolo (liloba na ndimbola), sangisa, landa molongo ya mayele, mpe yoka mongongo ya pronunciation. XP epesami na bokokisi.",
    "glossary_etymology_info": "Lakisa epai liloba ewutaki na misisa na yango. Esalisi mingi mpo na maloba ya Tier 3 ya siansi mpe makambo ya bato oyo ewuti na Greek to Latin. K-5 ezwaka maloba ya pete, 6-12 ezwaka prefix mpe root.",
    "timeline_visuals_info": "Sala bililingi ya AI mpo na eloko mokomoko na molongo. Esalisi bayekoli ya K-5 mpe ELL. Ebakisaka mwa ngonga na bosaleli; tika yango pembeni mpo na makanisi ya abstract.",
    "glossary_language_flashcards": "Sala flashcards ya minoko mibale: liloba na ekomami → libongoli na monoko ya mama. Mongongo ya pronunciation ezali na minoko nyonso mibale. Esalisi bayekoli ya ELL.",
    "glossary_export_standard": "Bimisá yo maloba flashcard as PDF ya kobimisa. eloko ebimi ezali na: nyonso liloba na ndimbola, front/kozonga karte layout, na cut molongo mpo na pete separation. Bimisá baponi: 4 karte per lokasa (large, pete na handle), 8 karte (mibeko size), to 12 (compact). PDF ezali formatted mpo na double-sided printing so fronts na backs align. Monene mpo na: offline study, kelasi sets, na moboti homework lisalisi. toli: Bimisá likoló cardstock mpo na durable physical flashcard.",
    "glossary_export_language": "Bimisá minoko mibale flashcard na liloba na nyonso mibale monoko. mokó mokó karte elakisaka: liloba na mokano monoko (front), libongoli na native monoko (kozonga), na pronunciation guide. lisalisi dual-monoko literacy development na ELL maloba building. Bimisá baponi match mibeko flashcard bimisá. Perfect mpo na: world monoko kelasi, minoko mibale programs, heritage monoko salela, na home-eteyelo connection mpo na multilingual families. Nyonso mibale monoko komonana na nyonso karte mpo na consistent paired koyekola. toli: Salelá these mpo na monoko-oyo study tángo na kotonga cross-linguistic connections.",
    "glossary_puzzle_lang": "Pona monoko mpo na puzzle: monoko ya yambo, monoko ya libongoli, to nyonso mibale. Pona ezali kobongola: kotanga liloba, makomi, mpe fungola ya biyano.",
    "glossary_word_search": "Sala puzzle ya koluka maloba na liste ya yo. Bongisa monene ya grille, mokakatano, mpe lolenge. Ebimisi na PDF ya kobimisa.",
    "glossary_memory_game": "Bandá ya bosolo Memory Match kosalela yo maloba. Gameplay: karte bandá face-down, finá two na flip, match liloba na ndimbola. misala: adjustable pair tángá (6-12 pairs), timed to untimed saná, matomba kolanda, na elilingi/mongongo liloba. Cognitive benefits: working memory salela, maloba reinforcement, na engagement na nzela lisano. XP awarded mpo na successful matches na bonus mpo na mbangu. karte shuffle mokó mokó lisano mpo na replay motuya. Esalaka na elilingi soki mokanda ya maloba ezali na elilingi. toli: Bandá na fewer pairs mpo na kobunda moyekoli, increase mpo na mpasi.",
    "glossary_crossword": "Sala crossword ya bonganga na maloba ya yo. AI esalaka clue na ndimbola, etia maloba malamu, mpe esalaka grille ya bonganga.",
    "glossary_matching": "Sala lisano ya kosangisa liloba na ndimbola. Benda mokolongo to finá pona mpo na kosangisa. Bipekiseli ya XP epesami na bosolo mpe mbangu.",
    "glossary_bingo": "Sala bakarte ya Bingo na maloba ya yo. Mokomoko moyekoli azwaka karte ya yango moko. Salaka maloba ya yo na kobimisa PDF.",
    "glossary_play_bingo": "Banda lisano ya Bingo ya digital na maloba ya yo. AI ekobenga ndimbola, mokomoko moyekoli atia elembo, mpe XP epesami na bolongi.",
    "glossary_scramble": "Lisano ya kobongisa maloba oyo elobami mabe. Komá liloba ya solo. Esalisi spelling mpe boyebi ya bilembo ya maloba.",
    "glossary_edit": "Fungola editor mpo na kobongisa liste ya maloba: bongisa nkombo, ndimbola, bakisa to longola, bongisa libongoli. Bobongisi nyonso ebombami yango moko.",
    "glossary_add_term": "Bakisá ya yo maloba liloba na mokanda ya maloba. Kotisá lolenge (e.g., 'cartoon', 'pixel art') na liloba na bakisá.",
    "glossary_image_style": "Define art lolenge mpo na AI-esalemi liloba elilingi (e.g., 'pixel art', 'cartoon', 'sketch').",
    "glossary_terms_table": "Talá na manage nyonso maloba liloba, ndimbola, libongoli, na elilingi.",
    "glossary_image_size": "Kobongisa size ya elilingi displayed na mokanda ya maloba.",
    "glossary_filter_all": "Lakisá nyonso liloba na mokanda ya maloba.",
    "glossary_filter_tier2": "Lakisa kaka maloba ya Tier 2 — maloba ya academic ya bonene koleka oyo ezali kobima na masolo nyonso (lolenge: bandela, lokanga, elembo).",
    "glossary_filter_tier3": "Lakisa kaka maloba ya Tier 3 — maloba ya technical ya domain (lolenge: photosynthesis, democracy). Esengeli koteya na ntango ya liteya.",
    "glossary_search": "Luka maloba ya yo na liste ya maloba. Komá ndambo ya liloba; bisaluki ezali komonana mbala moko. Eluka na nkombo, ndimbola, mpe libongoli.",
