    "header_settings_text": "Bongisá how makomi emonani throughout app. baponi bakisá: Font Family (poná OpenDyslexic mpo na reading difficulties, to Inter/Roboto mpo na clean readability), Font Size (increase mpo na low vision), molongo Spacing (bakisá vertical space kati molongo mpo na easier kolanda), Letter Spacing (spread letters apart mpo na dyslexia lisalisi), na Bionic Reading (bolds ya liboso few letters ya mokó mokó maloba na guide eye). nyonso mbongwana apply instantly na persist across tángo.",
    "header_settings_text_font": "Poná font family optimized mpo na readability.",
    "header_settings_text_size": "Kobongisa base font size mpo na application.",
    "header_settings_text_line_height": "Kobongisa vertical space kati molongo ya makomi.",
    "header_settings_text_spacing": "Kobongisa horizontal space kati letters.",
    "header_settings_text_bionic": "Fungola Bionic Reading: bilembo ya yambo ya liloba mokomoko ekomi makasi mpo na kosalisa kotanga noki. Esalisi bayekoli ya ADHD mpe ya botangi mpasi.",
    "header_settings_text_reset": "Bandá lisusu nyonso makomi bobongisi na ya ebandeli.",
    "header_settings_voice": "Configure makomi-na-speech mongongo bobongisi. Poná uta ebele AI voices (male/female, different accents), kobongisa Speaking mbangu (slower mpo na kososola, faster mpo na fluent readers), tiá volume niveau, na momekano voices before selecting. These bobongisi affect nyonso tángá-aloud misala elongo na 🔊 bouton likoló karte, Karaoke lolenge, na AlloBot's spoken responses. toli: Memá different voices na find one yo moyekoli responds na best.",
    "header_settings_voice_select": "Poná AI mongongo mpo na makomi-na-speech.",
    "header_settings_voice_speed": "Kobongisa speaking mbangu.",
    "header_settings_voice_volume": "Kobongisa volume.",
    "header_settings_anim": "Bongolá animations na reduce kotambola sensitivity.",
    "header_settings_theme": "Mbongwana elilingi appearance ya entire application. Light lolenge: White backgrounds, dark makomi—best mpo na well-lit rooms na bimisá-like reading. Dark lolenge: Dark backgrounds, light makomi—reduces eye strain na dim environments na conserves battery. Likoló Contrast: Yellow likoló black na bold fonts—designed mpo na low vision users, designed na meet WCAG bokokoki mibeko. yo preference ezali ebombami na persists across tángo. toli: Mosusu moyekoli focus malamu koleka na Dark lolenge as it reduces écran brightness distractions.",
    "header_settings_overlay": "Bakisa kobombama ya langi na etanda mobimba. Etamboli kati ya Bule, Lokombe, Bobongo, mpe te. Esalisi mosusu ya Irlen to dyslexia.",
    "header_view_teacher": "Fungola interface mobimba ya molakisi: kosalema, kotalela, analytics, kopesa note, mpe export. Esengaka kondima.",
    "header_view_student": "Lakisa interface ya bayekoli: activités, makomi, mpe XP. Ebombi bobongisi ya molakisi mpe ya likolo.",
    "header_dashboard": "Kotala dashboard ya analytics: bisaluki ya kelasi, mokomoko moyekoli, makanisi-niveau, XP, mpe export ya CSV/PDF.",
    "header_jump_lesson": "Zonga noki na Lesson Plan ya yo ya nsima. Ebombi ngonga na ntango ya kosalela bisaleli ya kosunga.",
    "header_bot_toggle": "Bongola visibilité ya AlloBot na etanda. Ekobomba avatar kasi etiká bot na nzela ya lisolo.",
    "header_cloud_sync": "Sync ya cloud ya mosala na yo. Soki ezali ON: bibombi ya yango moko, kotala uta na biloko mosusu. Bilembo ya status ekobima.",
    "header_tour_start": "Bandá ya bosolo, guided walkthrough ya current talá na misala.",
    "header_about": "Lakisa About: motángo ya version, ya sika misala, makomi ya privacy, mpe maboko ya kosolola.",
    "header_support": "lisalisi AlloFlow development na nzela donations to liloba. Ways na lisalisi: financial contributions lisalisi maintain servers na fund ya sika misala, liloba provides invaluable direction mpo na improvements, bug reports lisalisi us fix issues quickly, na sharing na colleagues expands our community. Developer contact sango ezali na Na tina lopangu. AlloFlow ezali developed by educators mpo na educators—yo lisalisi keeps project sustainable. nyonso contributions ezali appreciated regardless ya size. Consider: reporting bugs tángo yo find them, suggesting misala yo need, na kotala lisusuing updates na ndimá fixes work. toli: most valuable lisalisi ezali telling mosusu molakisi na tina AlloFlow.",
    "hints_recall": "Fungola historique ya toli ya contextual oyo AlloBot apesi yo. Toli etandami na molongo ya ngonga.",
    "xp_modal_trigger": "Fungolá yo XP na achievements dashboard na track yo lisano koyekola bokoli.",
