    "word_sounds_review_play_word": "Yoka ndenge liloba ekobengama na ntango ya activité. Esalelaka bobongisi ya mongongo ya yo.",
    "word_sounds_review_play_phonemes": "Hear mokó mokó moko na moko sound na maloba spoken separately, then blended. Mpo na maloba CAT: yo hear /k/... /æ/... /t/... then cat. Oyo demonstrates phoneme segmentation (breaking maloba na mingongo) na blending (combining mingongo na maloba)—two foundational mayele mpo na reading. mbangu adjusts automatically mpo na learner niveau. Etongaka phonemic awareness, single strongest predictor ya early reading elonga. Salelá mpo na: phonics malako, phonological awareness intervention, na lisalisiing kobunda readers connect letters na mingongo. Research elakisaka explicit phoneme malako improves decoding mayele.",
