    "persona_save_chat": "Bomba lisolo ya Persona mpo na kotala lisusu na nsima.",
    "analysis_check_accuracy": "AI-esalemi mateya can contain libunga. tángo enabled, adds ~5 segondes kasi cross-checks facts na Google Lukáká. Shows [✓ verified] to [⚠️ unverified] markers.",
    "persona_response_mode": "Bongolá kati 'Boponi Ebele' (easier) na 'Free Response' (fungolá-ended typing) interaction lolenge.",
