    "adventure_auto_climax": "Tika AI ekamba lisapo ya Adventure mpo na esuka ya makasi.",
    "adventure_cancel_new": "Tika kosala Adventure ya sika mpe zonga na Adventure ya kala.",
    "adventure_cloud_storage": "Tika données ya Adventure ebombama na cloud mpo na kosalela na ba appareils mosusu.",
    "adventure_confirm_new": "Ndima kosala Adventure ya sika. Ya kala ekobombama yango moko.",
    "adventure_lock_settings": "Pekisa bayekoli kobongola baparametres ya Adventure.",
    "adventure_low_quality": "Bongolá elilingi quality mpo na mobembo elilingi. Low quality: faster ekeke (2-3 segondes vs 8-10), lower API costs, smaller fichier sizes, na adequate mpo na most kelasi esalelaka. Likoló quality: mingi na mike-mike elilingi, malamu koleka mpo na printing, na showcase quality. Quality affects: resolution, mike-mike niveau, na artistic refinement. Low quality ezali often sufficient mpo na instructional purposes. Likoló quality ezali malamu koleka mpo na: elokod projects, printed biloko, na elilingi portfolios. bobongisi applies na ya sika generations only, existing elilingi unchanged. toli: Salelá low quality during liteya development, bongolá na likoló mpo na final version.",
    "adventure_story_mode": "Control lisapo richness na mobembos. tángo enabled: longer descriptive passages, deeper mosali na lisapo development, literary techniques, na mozindo storytelling. tángo disabled: straightforward mateya dena bomoiry, shorter makomi, na direct-motuna lolenge. lisapo lolenge etongaka: reading kososola, appreciation mpo na lisapo structure, na engagement na nzela immersion. Kangá mpo na: noki salela activities, kobunda readers, to tángo prioritizing mateya likoló lisapo. lisapo lolenge passages ezali auto-adjusted na reading niveau bobongisi. Nyonso mibale lolenge lisalisi curriculum mateya integration. toli: Fungolá mpo na literature connections, kangá mpo na mateya-focused kotala lisusu.",
    "export_html": "Bimisa lokola lokasa ya web (HTML) oyo ekoki kofungwama na nzela ya browser.",
    "export_ims": "Salá LMS-compatible package. IMS Na bokó Cartridge ezali mibeko lolenge recognized by: Canvas, Blackboard, Moodle, Schoology, na most koyekola management molongo. Package ezali na: nyonso mateya, momekano na eyano keys, na metadata mpo na organization. Kotisá na yo LMS na: assign na moyekoli, track kosukisa, na kelasi within yo existing molongo. Package contains: .imscc fichier ready mpo na tomá. Follow yo LMS malako mpo na importing cartridges. toli: IMS bimisá ezali most reliable way na integrate AlloFlow mateya na yo district LMS.",
    "export_qti": "Bimisa Quiz na lolenge ya QTI mpo na Canvas, Blackboard, Moodle, na ba LMS mosusu.",
    "export_slides": "Sala ba slides ya présentation (PowerPoint to PDF).",
    "export_storybook_images": "Bimisa bililingi nyonso ya Adventure na ZIP file.",
    "export_storybook_text": "Bimisa lisapo ya Adventure lokola mokanda ya makomi.",
    "export_worksheet": "Sala worksheet ya bayekoli oyo ekoki kobimisama na lokasa.",
    "fab_toggle": "Lakisa to bomba botouton ya Floating Action Button (FAB) mpo na biloko ya accessibilité.",
    "fab_dictation": "Convert speech na makomi mpo na hands-free eloko ekoti. Finá na activate microphone, lobá clearly, na talá maloba komonana. Esalaka na: makomi eloko ekoti, kokoma scaffolds, lisolo, na any editable field. lisalisi: ebele monoko, punctuation commands (say period, comma, ya sika molongo), na editing commands (bomá yango). Dictation requires microphone permission na browser. Quality depends likoló: microphone quality, background noise, na speech clarity. Ngonga ya solo transcription elakisaka as yo lobá. Bongisá transcribed makomi normally. Monene mpo na: moyekoli na motor mpasi, reluctant writers, na idea ekeke. toli: Lobá na silisá fraze mpo na malamu koleka bosolo.",
    "fab_focus": "Creates movable spotlight yango dims everything except circular surface around yo cursor. Oyo dramatically reduces elilingi clutter na lisalisis maintain attention likoló current reading surface. Especially beneficial mpo na moyekoli na ADHD, sensory processing differences, to anyone overwhelmed by busy screens. spotlight follows yo mouse/touch automatically. Kobongisa spotlight size na dim intensity na bobongisi → Bokokoki.",
