    "settings_persona_free": "Tika bayekoli bakoma yango moko mituna na Persona to bapona kati ya baoponi.",
    "settings_unlock_xp": "Configure XP esengeli na unlock special misala. ya ebandeli threshold provides achievable kasi meaningful tina. Higher thresholds: extend engagement, salá longer-liloba tina, na prevent early kokota. Lower thresholds: fungolá faster kokota, accommodate shorter programs, na reduce frustration mpo na kobunda moyekoli. Unlockable misala bakisá: ya yo likambo, special elembo, ya likolo biloko ya mosala, na premium customizations. XP unlocks salá anticipation na tina-bobongisi ezalela. Review unlock rates na analytics. soki few moyekoli reach thresholds, consider lowering. soki most unlock quickly, consider raising. toli: Tiá threshold achievable within yo program molayi so moyekoli mayele mbano.",
    "simplified_check_level": "Talela niveau ya kotanga ya makomi: Lexile, niveau ya kelasi, mpe Flesch-Kincaid.",
