    "concept_sort_game": "esalaka likanisi tia na molongo lisano interface mpo na categorization salela. Benda eloko na correct lisanga buckets na demonstrate understanding ya kelasiification makanisi. Immediate liloba elakisaka correct na incorrect placements. lisalisi 2-4 masanga na any motuya ya sortable eloko. Monene mpo na maloba tiers, science kelasiifications, to grammar sorting.",
