      "buffers": "🛡️ Ba-buffer",
      "titrate_find_the_equivalence_point": "Sala titration — Luka esika ya bokokani",
      "add_titrant_drop_by_drop_until_indicat": "Bakisa titrant litɔnga na litɔnga tii elakiseli ekobongola langi. Esika ya bokokani = bokokani ya stoichiometric; esika ya nsuka = epai elakiseli ebongwanaka. Ezali ndenge moko te ntango nyonso.",
      "challenge_graded_titrations": "Mokakatano — Ba-titration oyo epesami ba-note",
      "match_real_world_unknowns_by_titrating": "Kokanisa biloko oyo eyebani te ya mokili ya sɔlɔ na kosala titration tii ±0.05 ml ya motuya ya théorie. Landa bosikisiki + mbangu; kopesa ba-note ekokani na AP Chem.",
      "safety_drills_what_could_go_wrong": "Ba-momekano ya bokɛngɛli — Nini ekoki kobeba",
      "burette_explodes_acid_burns_spill_indi": "Biuret epaswuki, kopanzana ya kozika ya asidi, elakiseli ebakisami nokí mingi. Meka ba-suite ya eyano ya malamu liboso ekóma na ntina na laboratoire ya sɔlɔ.",
      "equipment_burette_flask_pipette": "Bisaleli — Biuret, flask, pipette",
      "burette_tolerance_0_05_ml_volumetric_f": "Boyokani ya biuret 0.05 ml; flask ya volume 0.10 ml; pipette 0.02 ml. Kelasi ya bosikisiki A na B ekómisaka libunga mbala mibale. Kobongisa ezali na ntina koleka ndenge banakelasi bakanisaka.",
      "dilution_calculator_m_v_m_v": "Esaleli ya kotanga ya kokwea — M₁V₁ = M₂V₂",
      "stock_diluent_desired_concentration_th": "Stock + eloko ya kokwisa → motango oyo balingi. Ba-problème 4 ya AP Chem oyo emekamaka mingi ekitaka na équation moko oyo. Landa bakisi ya ntina: momekano ya bolɛmbu koleka ekataka eyano.",
      "buffer_discovery_when_does_a_buffer_ho": "Bokundoli ya buffer — Ntango nini buffer eumelaka?",
      "adjust_acid_strength_a_ha_ratio_starti": "Bongisa makasi ya asidi, ratio ya [A⁻]/[HA], mpe pH ya ebandeli. Mbano ekeseni: buffer ya malamu to buffer ya mabe (nsima ya kobakisa asidi ya kobakisa 20%). Note ezali te, kolakisa ezali te — kaka bolukiluki mpe botali.",
      "endpoint_equivalence": "⚠ Esika ya nsuka ≠ esika ya bokokani. ",
      "good_indicator_choice": "✔ Boponi ya elakiseli ya malamu. ",
      "redox_titration_not_a_ph_curve": "⚗ Titration ya redox — courbe ya pH te. ",
      "the_trace_shows_relative_reaction_prog": "Molɔngɔ elakisaka bokoli ya réaction ya bokokani, pH te — mɛtrɛ ya pH ezali awa te. Esika ya nsuka ezali langi ya rose ya liboso ya pɛtɛpɛtɛ oyo eumelaka na koleka moke ya MnO₄⁻ (esalaka réaction violé → langi te tii na ntango wana). Tanga esika oyo ya nsuka na langi.",
