      "the_flat_part_of_a_weak_acid_base_curv": " — eteni ya platí ya courbe ya asidi/base ya bolɛmbu epai pH etɛmɛlaka mbongwana (Henderson–Hasselbalch esalaka).",
      "indicators": "Ba-elakiseli",
