      "600_000_sandhill_cranes_gather_here_ea": "Sandhill Cranes 600,000 basanganaka awa na eleko ya prɛnta mokomoko — moko ya bamonisi ya kitoko koleka ya bozalisi",
      "great_salt_lake": "Great Salt Lake",
      "5_million_migratory_birds_depend_on_th": "Bandɛkɛ ya mobembo milio 5 bayekamaka na mbu oyo ya mokili lokola esika ya botondisi-mafuta",
