      "wetlands_here_support_40_of_north_amer": "Mabelé ya mai awa esungaka 40% ya bandɛkɛ ya mai ya mobembo ya Amerika ya Nɔɔrdi",
      "chesapeake_bay": "Chesapeake Bay",
      "largest_estuary_in_the_us_critical_win": "Monɔkɔ ya ebale monene koleka na US — esika ya bofandi ya eleko ya malili ya ntina mpo na bana-libata mpe bandɛkɛ",
