      "fun_fact": "Likambo ya Kosepelisa: ",
      "the_four_north_american_flyways": "🗺️ Banzela Minei ya Bopimbwi ya Amerika ya Nɔɔrdi",
      "atlantic_2": "Atlantique",
      "mississippi_2": "Mississippi",
      "central_2": "Katikati",
      "pacific_2": "Pacifique",
      "when_do_birds_migrate": "📅 Ntango Nini Bandɛkɛ Basalaka Mobembo?",
      "migration_timing_varies_dramatically_b": "Ntango ya mobembo ekeseni mingi na kotalela lolenge:",
      "early_spring_waterfowl_ducks_geese_hea": "Ebandeli ya prɛnta: Bandɛkɛ ya mai (bana-libata, bandɛkɛ) bakendaka nɔɔrdi na kolanda konyangwa ya glasi. Red-winged Blackbirds bazongaka na mabelé ya mai.",
      "peak_spring_warblers_vireos_tanagers_f": "Bosanda ya prɛnta: Warblers, vireos mpe tanagers batondisaka nɔɔrdi. Bandɛkɛ mingi ya banzembo basalaka mobembo na butu. Na babutu ya likoló ezali koleka bandɛkɛ milio 500 na likoló.",
      "shorebirds_start_south_some_species_fa": "Bandɛkɛ ya libongo babandaka na sudi — balolenge mosusu “balongaka te” na bisika ya kobota mpe babandaka kozonga na ebandeli ya sanza ya Yuli. Bakóló mbala mingi bakendaka liboso ya bana.",
      "peak_fall_raptors_ride_thermals_along_": "Bosanda ya eleko ya matiti: Banyama ya boyemi bamataka mopɛpɛ ya molunge na molɔngɔ ya bangomba. Bandɛkɛ ya banzembo bakendaka sudi na kolanda bilongi ya malili. Bandɛkɛ bapimbwaka na molɔngɔ V na butu.",
      "photoperiod_day_length_is_the_primary_": "Bolai ya mokolo ezali ntina ya liboso ya mobembo. Ntango mikolo ekómi mikuse na eleko ya matiti, ba-hormone ebimisaka “Zugunruhe” — kozanga kimya ya mobembo — mpe bandɛkɛ babandaka kosangisa mafuta (koliya na koleka), ntango mosusu bakómisaka kilo ya nzoto mbala mibale.",
      "stopover_ecology": "⛺ Ekolozi ya Bisika ya Botelemi",
      "stopovers_are_not_just_rest_stops_they": "Bisika ya botelemi ezali kaka bisika ya bopemi te, ezali ",
      "refueling_stations": "bisika ya botondisi-mafuta",
      "critical_to_survival_a_migrating_warbl": " ya ntina mpo na bobiki. Warbler ya mobembo akoki kolekisa 75% ya ntango ya mobembo na bisika ya botelemi, koliya na ligboma mpo na kotonga lisusu mafuta. Esika ya bofandi ya botelemi ya malamu ekoki kozala bokeseni na kati ya bomoi mpe liwa.",
      "at_delaware_bay_over_1_million_shorebi": "Na Delaware Bay, koleka bandɛkɛ ya libongo milio 1 (Red Knots, Ruddy Turnstones, Sanderlings) bayekamaka na makei ya nkala ya farasa oyo babotamaki na Mayi. Ntango esengeli kozala malamu: bandɛkɛ bayaka kaka na ntango oyo bankala ya farasa babotaka makei. Soki motango ya bankala ya farasa ekiti (mpo na koboma mbisi na koleka mpo na esimbeli), monyɔlɔlɔ mobimba ya mobembo ekwei.",
      "conservation_success_story_after_horse": "Lisolo ya elonga ya bobateli: Nsima ya kokɔtisa bandelo ya bobuki ya bankala ya farasa na 2012, motango ya Red Knot ebandaki kozonga malɛmbɛ uta na nse ya mokakatano ya 15,000 tii koleka 50,000 na 2025.",
      "migration_physiology": "🦴 Fiziolozi ya Mobembo",
      "migration_is_one_of_the_most_physicall": "Mobembo ezali moko ya misala oyo esɛngaka nzoto mingi na bokonzi ya banyama. Bandɛkɛ balekaka na mbongwana ya nzoto ya kokamwa liboso ya kokende:",
      "hyperphagia": "Koliya na Koleka",
      "before_migration_birds_enter_a_feeding": "Liboso ya mobembo, bandɛkɛ bakɔtaka na koliya na koleka oyo babengaka hyperphagia, koliya na mbangu ya mbala 2-3 koleka momeseno. Blackpoll Warbler (gramu 12) ebakisaka mafuta ya gramu 8-12, pene ya kokómisa kilo ya nzoto mbala mibale. Mafuta oyo ezali esimbeli mpo na bopimbwi kozanga kotelema ya koleka bakilomɛtɛlɛ 2,000.",
      "organ_shrinkage": "Bokitisi ya Binama",
      "to_reduce_weight_migrating_birds_actua": "Mpo na kokitisa kilo, bandɛkɛ ya mobembo bakitisaka mpenza binama ya bonyangwisi (misɔpɔ, libale, esika ya koniata) tii na 40% liboso ya kokende. Ntango bakómaka na bisika ya botelemi, batongaka lisusu binama oyo nokinoki mpo na kotondisa mafuta. “Plastisite ya fenotipe” oyo ezali ya kokɛsɛna na banyama oyo bazali na mokongo.",
      "hemoglobin": "Hemoglobine",
      "high_altitude_migrants_like_bar_headed": "Basaleli ya mobembo ya bosanda likoló lokola Bar-headed Geese (oyo bapimbwaka mɛtɛlɛ 29,000 likoló ya Himalaya) bazali na hemoglobine ya kokɛsɛna oyo ezali na bolingi mingi mpo na oksize. Misuni na bango ezali na myoglobine ya kobakisa, mpe boike ya bankapilɛlɛ na bango ezali mbala mibale ya balolenge ya mabelé ya nse.",
      "sleep_in_flight": "Mpongi na Bopimbwi",
      "some_birds_can_sleep_while_flying_usin": "Bandɛkɛ mosusu bakoki kolala mpongi ntango bazali kopimbwa, na kosalela “mpongi ya ndambo-ya-mbóngó” — kokanga ndambo moko ya bɔɔngɔ na ngonga moko. Ba-Frigatebird bakomaki bazali kolala mpongi miniti 42 na mokolo na ntango ya bopimbwi ya mikolo 10 ya kokatisa mbu, kozwaka mpongi ya mikɛ ya basegonde 12 mokomoko.",
      "navigation_clock": "Sáa ya Botambwisi",
      "birds_maintain_an_internal_circadian_c": "Bandɛkɛ babatelaka sáa ya kati ya sirkadiɛ oyo ezali na bosikisiki ya kokamwa. Sáa oyo efutaka bomibongoli ya moi na likoló (bousɔlɛ ya moi oyo efutami na ntango) mpe elandaka mbongwana ya bileko ya bolai ya mokolo oyo ebimisaka ba-hormone ya mobembo.",
      "zugunruhe": "Zugunruhe",
      "zugunruhe_migration_restlessness_is_a_": "Zugunruhe (“kozanga kimya ya mobembo”) ezali ezaleli ya bizaleli epai bandɛkɛ ya mobembo oyo bakangami na kaje babɛtaka mapapu na litambwisi oyo balingaki kosala mobembo na bomoto, na ntango oyo balingaki kosala mobembo. Ezali hormone oyo etindaka mpe ekomami na gɛnɛ. Ata bandɛkɛ oyo bakolisami na lobɔkɔ oyo bazali na eksperiansi ya mobembo te bamonisaka Zugunruhe.",
      "species_comparison": "📊 Bokokanisi ya Balolenge",
