      "bernoulli_s_principle": "Mobeko ya Bernoulli",
      "as_air_speeds_up_its_pressure_drops_a_": "Ntango mopɛpɛ ezali kobakisa mbangu, botindi na yango ekitaka. Etando ya likoló ya lipapu oyo egumbami etindaka mopɛpɛ ete etiyola mbangu likoló koleka na nse. Oyo esalaka ",
      "lower_pressure_above": "botindi ya nse na likoló",
      "higher_pressure_below": "botindi ya likoló na nse",
      "the_wing_generating_lift": " ya lipapu, esalaka bokoli.",
      "p_pv_pgh_constant": "P + ½pv² + pgh = konstant",
      "angle_of_attack_stall": "Etumbu ya Botúki mpe Kotelema",
      "as_the_angle_of_attack_increases_lift_": "Ntango etumbu ya botúki ebakisamaka, bokoli ebakisamaka — tii na esika moko. ",
      "critical_angle": "Etumbu ya ntina",
      "stall_angle_airflow_separates_from_the": " (etumbu ya kotelema) soki eleki, botiyoli ya mopɛpɛ ekabwanaka na etando ya likoló. Lipapu ebungisaka botiyoli ya mopɛpɛ ya pɛtɛɛ, bokoli ekitaka makasi, mpe bobendi epumbwaka. Oyo ezali “kotelema”.",
      "current_wing_s_stall_angle": "Etumbu ya kotelema ya lipapu ya sikawa: ",
      "best_l_d_at": ". L/D ya malamu na: ",
      "lift_to_drag_ratio_l_d": "Ekokanisi ya Bokoli-na-Bobendi (L/D)",
      "l_d_measures_aerodynamic_efficiency_a_": "L/D emekaka boyeba ya aerodynamik. L/D ya likoló elimboli bokoli mingi na eteni moko ya bobendi. Ba-albatros bakómaka bakokanisi ya L/D ya boyike ya ",
      "meaning_20_pounds_of_lift_for_every_1_": " (elingi koloba balivre 20 ya bokoli mpo na livre 1 mokomoko ya bobendi), moko ya malamu koleka na bozalisi. Ba-glider ya lelo ",
      "induced_vs_parasite_drag": "Bobendi ya Botindami vs Bobendi ya Parasite",
      "induced_drag": "Bobendi ya botindami",
      "is_a_byproduct_of_creating_lift_the_wi": " ezali mbuma ya bosali ya bokoli: mikɛlɛ ya nsɔngɛ ya lipapu oyo bandɛkɛ basalelaka na molɔngɔ V. Ekitaka na mbangu. ",
      "parasite_drag": "Bobendi ya parasite",
      "comes_from_the_bird_s_body_pushing_thr": " euti na nzoto ya ndɛkɛ oyo ezali kotinda na mopɛpɛ; ebakisamaka na karé ya mbangu. Na esika ya bokutani ya bakurbe oyo mibale ezali ",
      "minimum_drag_speed": "mbangu ya bobendi ya moke koleka",
      "the_most_efficient_cruising_speed": " — mbangu ya mobembo ya malamu koleka.",
      "reynolds_number": "Motango ya Reynolds",
      "bird_flight_operates_at_reynolds_numbe": "Bopimbwi ya ndɛkɛ esalaka na mitango ya Reynolds na kati ya 10,000 mpe 500,000 — sistɛmɛ ya aerodynamik ya mpasi. Na bameko oyo, likutu ya ndelo (likutu ya moke ya mopɛpɛ oyo ekangami na etando ya lipapu) ezali ndambo laminaire, ndambo ya mobulu. Bansala ya bandɛkɛ esalaka mobulu-ya-mikɛ oyo mpenza ",
      "maintain_airflow_attachment_especially": " ebatelaka bokangani ya botiyoli ya mopɛpɛ, mingimingi na batumbu minene ya botúki. Oyo ezali likambo oyo ba-injenieur bazali naino koluka kosala lisusu na ba-plan ya drone.",
      "bio_inspired_engineering": "⚙️ Injenieri Oyo Bomoi Etindi",
      "bird_flight_has_inspired_countless_eng": "Bopimbwi ya ndɛkɛ etindaki bikelamu ya injenieri ebele oyo ekoki kotangama te:",
      "winglets": "Ba-Winglet",
      "the_upturned_wingtips_on_modern_airlin": "Bansɔngɛ ya mapapu oyo egumbami likoló na mpɛpɔ ya lelo ya bapaseze (Boeing 737 MAX, Airbus A350) eutaki mpenza na bansala ya nsɔngɛ oyo ekabwani ya bampongo. Ba-“winglet” oyo ekitisaka bobendi ya botindami na 5-7%, ebombelaka bakompanyi ya mpɛpɔ ba-miliaridi ya motuya ya esimbeli na mbula. Esalaka na kobuka mokɛlɛ ya nsɔngɛ ya lipapu.",
      "owl_quiet_fans": "Ba-Ventilateur ya Kimya lokola ya Esulungútu",
      "owl_feathers_have_a_serrated_leading_e": "Bansala ya esulungútu ezali na nsɔngɛ ya liboso ya bino, litonga ya etando lokola velur, mpe nsɔngɛ ya nsima ya bafranje, oyo elongo ekitisaka makɛlɛlɛ ya aerodynamik pene ya kimya. Ba-injenieur na GE mpe Dyson bamekolaki bilembo oyo na banzela ya turbine mpe ba-plan ya ventilateur, bakitisaka makɛlɛlɛ na koleka desibel 10.",
      "kingfisher_bullet_trains": "Bamasini-ya-nzela oyo Kingfisher Etindi",
      "the_shinkansen_bullet_train_s_nose_was": "Zolo ya masini-ya-nzela ya Shinkansen esalemaki lisusu nsima ya injenieur motali-bandɛkɛ Eiji Nakatsu amonaki ba-kingfisher kozinda uta na mopɛpɛ tii na mai kozanga kobwaka mai. Zolo ya lolenge ya monɔkɔ ya kingfisher ekitisaki bopanzani ya makɛlɛlɛ na 30% mpe bosaleli ya kura na 15% ntango masini-ya-nzela ebimaki na batunɛlɛ.",
      "morphing_wings": "Mapapu Oyo Ebongolaka Lolenge",
      "birds_continuously_adjust_wing_shape_a": "Bandɛkɛ babongisaka ntango nyonso lolenge ya lipapu, etumbu mpe esika ya nsala na ntango ya bopimbwi — na mayele koleka mpɛpɔ nyonso. NASA mpe MIT bazali kotomba tekiniki ya “lipapu oyo ebongolaka lolenge” oyo esalelaka biloko ya kobɛnda mpe ba-actuateur mpo na komekola bobongisi ya lipapu ya ndɛkɛ, na likoki ya kobongisa boyeba na 8-12%.",
      "feather_engineering": "🪶 Injenieri ya Nsala",
      "a_bird_feather_is_one_of_the_most_comp": "Nsala ya ndɛkɛ ezali moko ya bitongami ya mindɔndɔ koleka na bozalisi. Nsala ya bopimbwi ezali na:",
      "the_central_shaft_a_hollow_tube_strong": "Nzeté ya katikati — tiyo ya lidusu, makasi koleka ebende na ekokanisi ya kilo, esalemi na beta-keratine.",
      "hundreds_of_branches_growing_from_the_": "Nkama ya bitape oyo ebimaka na nzeté, esalaka etando ya nsala.",
      "tiny_hook_like_structures_connecting_b": "Bitongami ya mikɛ lokola bahameso oyo ekangisaka bitape lokola velcro. Nsala ya ebenga moko ezali na pene ya bahameso ya mikɛ milio 1.",
      "microscopic_hooks_on_barbules_that_zip": "Bahameso ya mikɛ mpenza na ba-barbule oyo ekangisaka bitape lokola fermeture, esalaka etando oyo mopɛpɛ ekoki koleka te. Ntango nsala epanzani, ndɛkɛ akoki kokangola yango na monɔkɔ na ye mpe “kokanga” yango lisusu.",
      "flight_feathers_are_asymmetric_the_lea": "Bansala ya bopimbwi ezali ndenge moko te — etando ya nsɔngɛ ya liboso ezali ya nkaka koleka nsɔngɛ ya nsima. Bokeseni oyo esalaka lolenge ya airfoil oyo egumbami oyo esalaka bokoli, lokola lipapu ya mpɛpɔ. Bansala ya liboso na bansɔngɛ ya mapapu ebalukaka na ntango ya kobɛta-na-nse, esalaka lokola bansala ya propelle moko na moko.",
      "birds_have_1_000_25_000_feathers_a_swa": "Bandɛkɛ bazali na bansala 1,000 tii 25,000 (swan ezali na ebele koleka). Babongolaka bansala na bango nyonso ya bopimbwi mbula na mbula na ntango ya ",
      "typically_after_breeding_season_and_be": ", mingimingi nsima ya eleko ya kobota mpe liboso ya mobembo. Kobungisa bansala mingi na ngonga moko ekoki kosala ete ndɛkɛ apimbwa te, yango wana bokwei ya bansala elandaka bokokani ya bangámbo mibale ya sikisiki: bansala oyo ekokani na lipapu mokomoko ebongwanaka na ngonga moko.",
      "migration_energy_budget": "⚡ Bozwi ya Nguya ya Mobembo",
      "consider_a_ruby_throated_hummingbird_c": "Kanisá Ruby-throated Hummingbird oyo azali kokatisa Gulf ya Mexico (bakilomɛtɛlɛ 500 kozanga kotelema):",
      "body_mass_3_5g": "Kilo ya nzoto: gramu 3.5",
      "pre_flight_fat_2g_57_body_weight": "Mafuta liboso ya bopimbwi: +gramu 2 (57% ya kilo ya nzoto!)",
