      "crossing_time_20_hours_at_25_mph": "Ntango ya kokatisa: ~bangonga 20 na 25 mph",
      "energy_required_16_kcal": "Nguya oyo esengeli: ~16 kcal",
      "margin_of_safety_2_kcal_11": "Ndelo ya bokengi: ~2 kcal (11%)",
      "that_is_an_incredibly_thin_margin_a_st": "Yango ezali ndelo ya nkaka mpenza ya kokamwa. Mopɛpɛ ya liboso ya makasi, elongi ya malili, to kokóma na libongo na kozanga kilo ya 10% ekoki kozala liwa. Yango wana boyeba ya esika ya bofandi ya botelemi ezali ",
      "literally_life_or_death": "likambo ya bomoi to liwa mpenza",
      "for_migratory_birds": " mpo na bandɛkɛ ya mobembo.",
      "push_through_the_weather": "Tinda na kati ya ntango",
      "find_shelter_and_wait": "Luká ebombamelo mpe zelá",
      "detour_around": "Zinga zinga",
      "keep_flying": "Kobá kopimbwa",
      "land_and_rest": "Kitá mpe pemá",
      "ride_thermals": "Matá mopɛpɛ ya molunge",
      "animated_night_sky_showing_nocturnal_b": "Likoló ya butu ya animasion emonisaka mobembo ya bandɛkɛ ya butu. Minzoto engɛngaka zingazinga ya Monzoto ya Nɔɔrdi, milɔngɔ ya elanga ya aiman egumbamaka na likoló, mpe etuluku moke ekatisaka na elilingi. Emonisaka ndenge bandɛkɛ basalelaka minzoto mpe boyeba ya aiman mpo na botambwisi ya butu.",
      "how_birds_navigate": "🧭 Ndenge Bandɛkɛ Batambolaka",
