      "trailing_birds_catch_the_upwash_from_t": "Bandɛkɛ ya nsima bakangaka mopɛpɛ-likoló ya ndɛkɛ oyo azali liboso — libombo ya nguya 20-30%. Esika ya bokambi ebalukaka mpo ndɛkɛ oyo azali liboso asalaka mosala mingi koleka.",
      "wind_currents_thermals": "Mikɛlɛ ya Mopɛpɛ + Mopɛpɛ ya Molunge",
      "birds_read_pressure_gradients_we_canno": "Bandɛkɛ batangaka ba-gradient ya botindi oyo biso tokoki koyoka te. Mopɛpɛ-likoló, mokɛlɛ ya nsɔngɛ mpe makonzí ya molunge ezali nzela oyo banyama ya boyemi bapimbwaka bakilomɛtɛlɛ nkama batumbaka pene ya kalori zɛro.",
      "migration_routes_flyways": "Banzela ya Mobembo + Banzela ya Bopimbwi",
      "four_major_north_american_flyways_paci": "Banzela minei ya minene ya bopimbwi ya Amerika ya Nɔɔrdi (Pacifique, Katikati, Mississippi, Atlantique) etambwisaka ba-miliaridi ya bandɛkɛ mbala mibale na mbula. Maine ezali na likoló ya nzela ya bopimbwi ya Atlantique.",
      "aerodynamics_of_bird_flight": "Siansi ya Bokɛli ya Mopɛpɛ ya Bopimbwi ya Ndɛkɛ",
      "wing_shape_aspect_ratio_camber_tunes_l": "Lolenge ya lipapu (ekokanisi ya lolenge + bogumbami) ebongisaka bokoli na kotalela bobendi. Bandɛkɛ ya kopimbwa = ekokanisi ya lolenge ya likoló, kobɛta lipapu ya malɛmbɛ. Ba-hummingbird = ekokanisi ya lolenge ya nse, kobɛta lipapu koleka 60 Hz.",
